Material Outlined
Our consistent Material Outline icon pack follows the Material guidelines from Google, including the latest icon themes (filled, outlined, rounded, two tone, and sharp versions for each icon). All themes are pixel perfect at 24×24 pixels.
These system icons cover a variety of common actions, files, devices, objects, and directories.
Material icon pack succeeds the previous icon pack for Android Ice Cream.
Download free Material Outline icons on various themes for Android user interface design. The graphics are available in both png and vector.
As well, welcome to check new icons and popular icons in 30+ design styles.
